@using RandomWorkings.github.io.Components.Shared;
@page "/fungrounds/sharkhunt"
<PageTitle>P32 Fungrounds</PageTitle>

<div id="rw-shark-hunt" class="rw-fungrounds">

    <PageHeader Text="Shark Hunt" ImageSource="images/fungrounds/p32-shark.svg" />

    <TabControl>
        <TabPage TabLabel="What is Shark Hunt?">
            <p>
                Shark Hunt is a game of Chase, with punching.
            </p>
            <p>
                All are your competition in this mode, as you race to be the person who catches and lands the crippling blow on a fleeing Landshark (they probably deserved it).
            </p>

            <div class="learnings">
                <p><b>"Secret Training"</b></p>
                <p>Spotting Enemies.</p>
                <p>Sound Play.</p>
            </div>
        </TabPage>
        <TabPage TabLabel="Match Procedure">
            <ul>
                <li>Join the match lobby.</li>
                <li class="nested-list">
                    <ul>
                        <li>The password will be provided via stream chat and discord.</li>
                        <li><b>Do Not</b> join the last team on the list unless you are playing the role of the landshark. It would defeat the purpose of the game.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div>Jump from the plane and make your way to Ripton on the Southeastern side of Deston.</div>
                    <div class="graphic-with-caption">
                        <p>Figure 1 (Below): Location of Ripton.</p>
                        <img id="shark-hunt-Ripton" src="images/fungrounds/shark-hunt-Ripton.jpg" alt="Map showing Ripton's location on Deston" loading="lazy" />
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>On the way, pick up a few Self AEDs and Med Kits in case of accidents during the chase.</li>
                <li class="nested-list">
                    <ul>
                        <li><b>Please</b> refrain from picking up any C4, these are for the landshark to use as a starting signal.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div>Arrive at Ripton and head to the lower roof of this designated start location and take part in some warm-up dancing.</div>
                    <div class="graphic-with-caption">
                        <p>Figure 2 (Below): Designated Start Locations</p>
                        <a href="images/fungrounds/shark-hunt-start-location-picture.jpg" target="_self" class="link">
                            <img id="shark-hunt-start-location-picture" src="images/fungrounds/shark-hunt-start-location-picture.jpg" alt="Map showing designated start location within Ripton" loading="lazy" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>Once everyone has arrived, the landshark will go up to the higher roof and throw smoke grenades down onto the other competitors.</li>
                <li class="nested-list">
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <div>The landshark will be dressed in the following attire to make it easier to spot/identify them.</div>
                            <div class="graphic-with-caption">
                                <p>Figure 3 (Below): The Landsharks Attire.</p>
                                <img id="shark-hunt-costume" src="images/fungrounds/shark-hunt-costume.jpg" alt="The clothing combination the player acting as the landshark will wear. A shark mascot head with bright green and white clothing" loading="lazy" />
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Once the final smoke clears the chase begins.</li>
                <li class="nested-list">
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <div>The landshark can flee anywhere within the following boundaries.</div>
                            <div class="graphic-with-caption">
                                <p>Figure 4 (Below): The Limits of the Hunting Grounds.</p>
                                <a href="images/fungrounds/shark-hunt-limits.jpg" target="_self" class="link">
                                    <img id="shark-hunt-limits" src="images/fungrounds/shark-hunt-limits.jpg" alt="Map showing designated start location within Ripton" loading="lazy" />
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>

            <div class="winCondition">

                <p><b>Win Conditions</b></p>
                <p>The winner is the one to land the punch that 'knocks' the shark. (Try not killing them)</p>
                <p><b>OR</b></p>
                <p>The shark wins if they survive the entire match time.</p>

            </div>
        </TabPage>

        <TabPage TabLabel="Rules of Engagement">
            <ul>
                <li>As the landshark, <b>Do Not</b> purposefully leave the hunting ground limits.</li>
                <li>As the landshark, <b>Do Not</b> use the ascenders as hiding spots.</li>
            </ul>
        </TabPage>

